data.title: Who is registered for The Hundred Men's Draft 2024, Powered by Sage?
data.meta_description: Ahead of The Hundred Draft, Powered by Sage on 20 March, check out the list of every player available for selection.
data.text:
NEWS

Ahead of The Hundred Draft, Powered by Sage on 20 March, check out the list of every player available for selection.

The Hundred Draft, Powered by Sage is coming. Wednesday 20 March is the key date for you. That's when the eight teams, across both the women's and men's competitions, will continue building out their squads.

You can see how the squads are shaping up so far by clicking here.

In the Men's Competition, there are 252 domestic players and 394 overseas players registered for selection.

List of Women's Competition players registered

Every player has a reserve price. This is the minimum amount of money that a team can pay for them. If all teams fill their slots at that price band and above, then that player can no longer be selected.

Still trying to get your head around The Hundred Draft, Powered by Sage? We've got you. Click here for all the info.

Below is the list of every player registered. Alongside each of the overseas players is the country they represent at international level. Alongside each of the domestic players is the county they represent. Note that some players do not have a county.
